DESCRIPTION:Join Zoom Meeting\nhttps://seagroup.zoom.us/j/2795657091\nMeeting ID: 279 565 7091\n\nThis session is a 1.5h introduction to the SMART platform\, hosted by Winar.\n\nOptional if you have attended previous trainings or are already competent with SMART.\n\nPre-requisite: Access to SMART (https://smart.shopee.io/apps?tab=workspace). If you don't have access yet\, DM Winar.\n\nBring: Laptop & charger\n\nAgenda:\n1. Introduction to AI Agents\n2. AI Project Showcase\n3. Introduction to SMART Platform\n4. Agent Prompts and Prompting 101\n5. Knowledge Base & Tools\n6. Hands-on\n7. Agent Release\n8. Other Orchestration Modes\n\nSMART Platform Documentation:\nhttps://confluence.shopee.io/x/aa15ow
